  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tamil Nadu fishermen have thanked the Sri Lankan Navy",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The fishermen of Tamil Nadu have thanked the Sri Lankan Navy for rescuing and feeding the fishermen of Tamil Nadu who were stranded in the sea after their boat broke down in the sea between Dhanushkodi and Thalaimannar.",
        "06 fishermen in a boat owned by a Raja from Rameswaram area of \u200b\u200bTamil Nadu were catching fish between Dhanushkodi and Thalaimannar when the engine of the boat suddenly broke down and the fishermen were stranded on the boat.",
        "The Sri Lankan Navy patrolling the area noticed the Tamil Nadu fishermen and tried to fix the engine of the fishermen's boat while the Tamil Nadu fishermen were unable to do so.",
        "So despite trying to call boat engine repairers from Mannar Naval Base, it was of no avail.",
        "After that, the fishermen and their boat were brought to Mannar area and after feeding the fishermen there, the marines informed the boat owner in Irameswaram.",
        "According to information, after the boat owner and others visited the international waters, the marines handed over the fishermen and their damaged boat to them.",
        "The owner of the boat thanked the marines and returned to Rameswaram after rescuing the boat and the fishermen.",
        "When the Sri Lankan Navy approached them, they feared that they would be arrested. But the fishermen said that they thanked the navy for not arresting us but saving our lives, feeding us and handing over the boat and us."
      ],
